The paper describes a method for visual object detection, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method uses decision trees, which are a popular machine learning technique (cs.LG). The paper also discusses optimization and sensitivity to noise, which are common topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper provides experimental analysis through a face detection problem, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
